text: The 1961 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1961 NCAA University Division football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by third-year head coach Wayne Hardin. ==Schedule== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen
